Style:

1. VUE Global SCSS Variables
2. remove & add ampersand in scss where unnecessary or necessary
3. Remove unnecessary classes, replace them with already existing selectors e.g.: remove .section and use the section tag instead etc
4. Customize custom classes rather than bootstrap classes
5. Make every styling file to scss
6. Make sidenav into flexbox

Anti vue:

- Get rid of jquery, and use bootstrap's vue version
https://bootstrap-vue.org<https://bootstrap-vue.org/>
- Use computed instead stuff like this: this.$refs.sortby.innerText = target.innerText
- Vuex store instead window variables
- Unsubscribe from events
- make :class parameters more effective 
- make the formatting unified (" => ', function(){} => ()=>{} etc )